; Doorway-threshold visual. Authored at the DEFAULT trigger_size (48x16);
; RoomGate._sync_visual_to_trigger resizes it at runtime to the room's actual
; trigger_size (production rooms override to 48x80) so it reads as the full
; doorway opening, not a small floating bar. Color is the dark stone-brown of
; the chunk floor/wall seam (Color(0.102,0.071,0.063,*)) so the threshold reads
; as doorway masonry rather than a stray red artifact — red-bar fix, ticket
; 86ca3kpzz Stage-1 soak (Sponsor 2026-06-03).
[node name="Sprite" type="ColorRect" parent="."]
